# Shared, version-controlled on-entry setup (see the global ~/.claude direnv
# convention). Each clone keeps a thin, untracked local `.envrc` that just
# `source_env`s this file.
#
# `use flake` loads the Nix dev shell, which provides the lint/hygiene tools and
# installs the git hooks. (The Rust checker's toolchain, and the Lean seam after
# it, join the flake when they land.)
use flake
